| # | Title | Summary |
|---|-------|---------|
| I | [Zero as Singularity & Mobium as Finite Infinity](papers/WP_I_zero_singularity_mobium.md) | Redefines zero as undivided origin and infinity as a finite closed loop |
| II | [Additive Kernels & the Ternary Recursion Engine](papers/WP_II_additive_kernels.md) | Defines the four integer-only kernels that drive all recursion |
| III | [Boundary Folding: Inverse Mitosis Without Division](papers/WP_III_boundary_folding.md) | Locates centers without cutting — division-free measurement |
| IV | [Prime-Base Mitosis & Infinitely Scalable Rulers](papers/WP_IV_prime_base_mitosis.md) | Extends subdivision to any odd-prime base for infinite precision |
| V | [Discrete Cosmology: Mobium Time & Leap-Fold Calendars](papers/WP_V_mobium_time.md) | Integer-only 13×28 calendar system with built-in leap correction |
| VI | [Nested Dimensions & 4D Field Dynamics](papers/WP_VI_nested_dimensions.md) | Dimensions as emergent tiers of substance, not coordinate axes |
| VII | [Cosmic Breath: Four-Phase Universal Recursion](papers/WP_VII_cosmic_breath.md) | Replaces Big Bang with eternal four-phase respiration cycle |
